    Notebooks -->|codeserver| CodeServerDep
    Notebooks -->|rstudio| RStudioDep
    Notebooks -->|rstudio| R
    Notebooks -->|codeserver build| NodeJS

    %% ML Framework Dependencies
    subgraph MLFrameworks["ML Frameworks (Conditional)"]
        PyTorch["PyTorch 2.10"]
        TensorFlow["TensorFlow<br/>Latest"]
        LLMCompressor["LLM Compressor"]
        TrustyAI["TrustyAI<br/>+ Java 17 OpenJDK"]
        Elyra["Elyra 4.3.1"]
    end

    Notebooks -->|pytorch variants| PyTorch
    Notebooks -->|tensorflow variants| TensorFlow
    Notebooks -->|llmcompressor variant| LLMCompressor
    Notebooks -->|trustyai variant| TrustyAI
    Notebooks -->|datascience+ workbenches| Elyra

    %% GPU Dependencies
    subgraph GPUDeps["GPU Acceleration (Conditional)"]
        CUDA["CUDA Toolkit<br/>12.8-13.0"]
        ROCm["ROCm 7.1"]
    end

    Notebooks -->|cuda variants| CUDA
    Notebooks -->|rocm variants| ROCm

    %% Infrastructure Dependencies
    subgraph InfraDeps["Infrastructure"]
        nginx["nginx 1.24"]
        httpd["httpd (Apache) 2.4"]
        uv["uv 0.10.9-0.11.7"]
        mongocli["mongocli"]
        oc["OpenShift CLI (oc)"]
    end

    Notebooks -->|codeserver, rstudio| nginx
    Notebooks -->|codeserver, rstudio| httpd
    Notebooks -->|all images| uv
    Notebooks -->|datascience+| mongocli
    Notebooks -->|all workbenches| oc

    %% Internal RHOAI Platform Dependencies
    subgraph InternalDeps["Internal RHOAI Platform"]
        Operator["rhods-operator /<br/>opendatahub-operator"]
        Dashboard["ODH Dashboard"]
        NotebookCtrl["ODH Notebook Controller<br/>(kubeflow)"]
        DSP["Data Science Pipelines<br/>(DSPA)"]
        Culler["Notebook Controller<br/>Culler"]
    end

    Operator -->|deploys ImageStreams<br/>from manifests/| Notebooks
    Dashboard -->|reads annotations<br/>for workbench UI| Notebooks
    NotebookCtrl -->|resolves image,<br/>injects sidecar,<br/>mounts CA bundles| Notebooks
    DSP -->|mounts pipeline<br/>runtime config| Notebooks
    Culler -->|polls /api/kernels/<br/>for idle detection| Notebooks

    %% Build & Registry Dependencies
    subgraph BuildDeps["Build & Distribution"]
        Konflux["Konflux CI<br/>(hermetic builds)"]
        Registry["registry.redhat.io"]
        QuayIO["quay.io/opendatahub<br/>(ODH only)"]
        BuildConfig["OpenShift BuildConfig<br/>(RStudio only)"]
    end

    Konflux -->|builds images| Notebooks
    Notebooks -->|published to| Registry
    Notebooks -->|ODH images at| QuayIO
    BuildConfig -->|on-cluster build<br/>RStudio| Notebooks

